column5: my dad and i are headed up toward the karwarthas this Saturday, we plan on making stops at Scugog River, Lower Buckhorn and Burleigh Falls area, mainly shore fishing, bass? walleye? any tips?
Enjoy yourself, I think from your time around here you have all the knowledge you might need.  Bring some pictures back, 'k?
LOL dsn  we ended up not going, cause of transportation problems, o well, nest week
